07:12.699 --> 07:15.400
can I ask you
a totally random question?

07:15.402 --> 07:16.301
Anything, sweetie.

07:16.303 --> 07:19.171
Well, I have
a really big favor to...

07:19.173 --> 07:19.971
ERICA: (LAUGHING) Mom!

07:19.973 --> 07:21.473
