I love you, snuggle, snuggle!

07:25.813 --> 07:26.978
Aah! Oh, yes!

07:26.980 --> 07:28.814
My baby's going to college!

07:28.816 --> 07:31.950
What? No!
No, no, no, no.

07:31.952 --> 07:33.185
Adam, be happy
for your sister.

07:33.187 --> 07:35.287
This is a huge day.
No, no, no, no, no!

07:35.289 --> 07:37.889
Don't make it about me.
It's your day, Mommy.

07:37.891 --> 07:39.825
No! No, no, no, no, no, no!

07:39.827 --> 07:41.660
Emory may be
a thousand miles away,

07:41.662 --> 07:46.631
but with the love
of my children
and 20 flights a year,

07:46.633 --> 07:47.999
we will manage.

07:48.001 --> 07:48.633
(LAUGHS)

07:48.635 --> 07:50.902
I'm gonna get
my pilot's license.

07:50.904 --> 07:51.636
Boop!
(LAUGHS)

07:51.638 --> 07:53.805
Um, Mama, know what else
is exciting?

07:53.807 --> 07:56.842
Jackie invited me
down the shore next weekend.

07:56.844 --> 07:57.542
Oh, no, no.

07:57.544 --> 07:59.010
Your sister is going
away to college.

07:59.012 --> 08:01.346
That's enough excitement
for one Mother's Day.

08:01.348 --> 08:03.548
But I made up
a whole tap routine

08:03.550 --> 08:06.818
celebrating my love for you
on this special day.

08:09.790 --> 08:10.388
Yeah!

08:10.390 --> 08:14.059
You love your little
baby boopie tapping
his piggy wiggies.

08:14.061 --> 08:15.427
<i> ¶ Adappa-dappa-doo</i>

08:15.429 --> 08:17.496
<i> ¶ Adappa dappa da dappa ¶</i>

