08:23.604 --> 08:25.537
<i> ¶ Emory, Emory ¶</i>

08:25.539 --> 08:26.838
(CHUCKLES)

08:30.310 --> 08:31.610
ADULT ADAM:
<i> While everyone was afraid</i>

08:31.612 --> 08:32.844
<i> our president</i>
<i> would lead us to war,</i>

08:32.846 --> 08:36.047
<i> my big bro would lead</i>
<i> his loved ones to safety.</i>

08:36.049 --> 08:38.316
Fellow members of the JTP...
ALL: JTP!

08:38.318 --> 08:40.619
...and the love
of my life, Lainey...
ALL: Lainey!

