some bad ones.

09:07.648 --> 09:09.581
Super useful.
Next, Naked Rob.

09:09.583 --> 09:13.285
What skills do you have?
And don't say "being naked."

09:13.487 --> 09:13.885
Come back to me.

09:13.887 --> 09:17.556
Andy, clearly you're in,
