for shelling nuts.

09:19.192 --> 09:20.325
Plus, you can sleep
in a drawer.

09:20.327 --> 09:23.061
Very insulted, but
it's more important to live.

09:23.063 --> 09:25.564
Matt Bradley,
looks like you're in
serious trouble here.

09:25.566 --> 09:27.399
I was an Eagle Scout
and a lifeguard,

09:27.401 --> 09:28.733
