<i> I'd manipulate my mom</i>

10:36.236 --> 10:39.104
<i> with an even-more-epic</i>
<i> Mother's Day video.</i>

10:39.106 --> 10:40.505
Whatcha up to,
schmoopa-lumpa?

10:40.507 --> 10:44.142
Oh, I'm just finishing up
a little goodbye video
for Erica.

10:44.144 --> 10:44.676
Aww.

10:44.678 --> 10:45.810
It's a little early
for goodbyes,

