with you next weekend.

15:08.475 --> 15:09.841
That's amazing!

15:10.010 --> 15:11.276
You ruined my life!

15:11.278 --> 15:12.844
Erica, how are things,
dear sister?

15:12.846 --> 15:15.113
What's going on?
Well, your little beach bud
made it

15:15.115 --> 15:17.248
so that I can't go
to the college of my dreams

15:17.250 --> 15:20.184
just so he can suck face
with you in the sand.

15:20.353 --> 15:21.052
Her words!

15:21.054 --> 15:21.819
But I wouldn't be
opposed to it.

15:21.821 --> 15:25.657
I hope it was worth it,
because you just
lost a sister.

15:27.127 --> 15:29.227
My Teddy Grahams!
Uh, what was that?

15:29.229 --> 15:31.029
They're little
graham-cracker cookies

15:31.031 --> 15:31.796
shaped like teddy bears.

15:31.798 --> 15:33.531
No, I know what Teddy Grahams
are, Adam.

15:33.533 --> 15:34.299
I meant with your sister.

15:34.301 --> 15:37.001
I kinda made a video
that ruined college for her

15:37.003 --> 15:38.569
so we could hit the beach.

15:38.571 --> 15:40.171
Anyway, does it get cold
at night?

15:40.173 --> 15:42.540
Should I bring a jacket?
Um, that's horrible.

15:42.542 --> 15:43.975
Yeah, it doesn't sound
that great

15:43.977 --> 15:44.642
