15:44.644 --> 15:46.511
Maybe a windbreaker,
'cause the ocean breeze.

15:46.513 --> 15:50.782
I actually think it's best
that I do my own thing
for a while.

15:50.984 --> 15:52.717
(¶¶¶)

15:56.022 --> 15:57.055
ADULT ADAM:
<i> After his talk with Pops,</i>

15:57.057 --> 16:01.826
<i> Barry was determined</i>
<i> to brilliantly trick my dad</i>
<i> into building a bunker.</i>

16:01.828 --> 16:04.295
Hey! What the hell?
Sorry, had a hard day.

16:04.297 --> 16:06.464
Thought I'd catch up
on some world events

16:06.466 --> 16:07.799
by listening to the radio.

16:07.801 --> 16:10.969
BARRY: (MIMICS BEEPING)
<i> This is not a test</i>

16:10.971 --> 16:12.770
<i> of the Emergency Broadcast</i>
<i> System.</i>

16:12.772 --> 16:16.140
Oh, no, this is real
and completely serious,

16:16.142 --> 16:17.442
'cause the newscaster
said so!

16:17.444 --> 16:19.344
<i> We have confirmation</i>
<i> from President Reagan</i>

16:19.346 --> 16:22.313
<i> that Russia has launched</i>
<i> a bunch of nukes</i>
<i> at Jenkintown,</i>

16:22.315 --> 16:23.948
<i> just like in</i>
<i> that movie we all saw.</i>

16:23.950 --> 16:26.184
<i> It's happening right now</i>
<i> as we speak,</i>

16:26.186 --> 16:27.785
<i> live, here in the '80s.</i>

16:27.787 --> 16:30.688
I know, Dad.
This is a very scary moment.

16:30.690 --> 16:33.758
It's so real,
I don't know what to do.

16:33.760 --> 16:38.029
Ha! I only made
that incredibly
authentic newscast

16:38.031 --> 16:40.331
to scare you
into seeing the truth.

16:40.333 --> 16:43.568
I told you you're not
building a dopey bunker
in the basement.

16:43.570 --> 16:45.103
Thank you
for keeping an open mind.

16:45.105 --> 16:47.005
I will also need money
for the following items.

16:47.007 --> 16:50.842
"Seven hundred pounds
of poured concrete,
lifetime supply of potatoes,

16:50.844 --> 16:53.177
"seven bottles of ketchup
for the potatoes..."

16:53.179 --> 16:55.613
There's one in the fridge.
Just take that and go.

16:55.615 --> 16:56.881
There's more.
We need, "A chicken,

16:56.883 --> 17:00.251
"a cage for the chicken,
medicine for the chicken,

17:00.253 --> 17:01.552
"a chicken exercise-wheel,

17:01.554 --> 17:03.921
"a lady chicken to keep
the other chicken company."

17:03.923 --> 17:07.392
Please stop asking me to build
a life for this chicken!

17:07.394 --> 17:09.761
Did he say yes
to the bunker?
I said no!

17:09.763 --> 17:11.162
Did you tell him
about the chicken?

17:11.164 --> 17:12.764
I don't wanna hear
about the chicken!

17:12.766 --> 17:14.298
