<i> Not because</i>
<i> she held us close,</i>

18:55.835 --> 18:58.769
<i> but because</i>
<i> she learned to let go.</i>

18:58.771 --> 19:00.838
<i> As for my dad,</i>
<i> he finally realized</i>

19:00.840 --> 19:02.373
<i> just what Barry</i>
<i> needed to hear.</i>

19:02.375 --> 19:06.177
Listen, I was thinking
about what you said.

19:06.179 --> 19:08.613
And the truth is,
I'm scared, too.

19:08.615 --> 19:10.848
You are?
I'm terrified!

