All I wanna do
is protect my family,

19:12.485 --> 19:14.752
and the thought that I might
not be able to do it,

19:14.754 --> 19:16.687
that keeps me up at night.

19:17.056 --> 19:20.024
So, what do we do?
Nothing.

19:20.193 --> 19:22.126
You just gotta live
the life you got

19:22.128 --> 19:23.494
and keep
the ones you love close.

